#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.138"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.138:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.138:0.2"
msgid "14. Puggalavagga"
msgstr "14. Persons"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: nikaṭṭhapuggalasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.138:0.3"
msgid "138. Nikaṭṭhasutta"
msgstr "138. Retreat"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.138:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.138:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.138:1.3"
msgid ""
"Nikaṭṭhakāyo anikaṭṭhacitto, anikaṭṭhakāyo nikaṭṭhacitto, anikaṭṭhakāyo ca "
"anikaṭṭhacitto ca, nikaṭṭhakāyo ca nikaṭṭhacitto ca."
msgstr ""
"~One is on retreat in body, but not mind; ~one is on retreat in mind, but "
"not body; ~one is on retreat in neither body nor mind; and ~one is on "
"retreat in both body and mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.138:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo hoti anikaṭṭhacitto?"
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in body, but not mind?"

#. VAR: araññavanapatthāni → araññe vanapatthāni (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.138:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person frequents remote lodgings in the wilderness and the "
"forest."

msgctxt "an4.138:2.3"
msgid ""
"So tattha kāmavitakkampi vitakketi byāpādavitakkampi vitakketi "
"vihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi."
msgstr "But they think sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts."

msgctxt "an4.138:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo hoti anikaṭṭhacitto."
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in body, but not mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.138:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo hoti nikaṭṭhacitto?"
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in mind, but not body?"

msgctxt "an4.138:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo naheva kho araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and "
"the forest."

msgctxt "an4.138:3.3"
msgid ""
"So tattha nekkhammavitakkampi vitakketi abyāpādavitakkampi vitakketi "
"avihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi."
msgstr "But they think thoughts of renunciation, love, and kindness."

msgctxt "an4.138:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo hoti nikaṭṭhacitto."
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in mind, but not body."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.138"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.138:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti anikaṭṭhacitto ca?"
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in neither body nor mind?"

msgctxt "an4.138:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo naheva kho araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and "
"the forest."

msgctxt "an4.138:4.3"
msgid ""
"So tattha kāmavitakkampi vitakketi byāpādavitakkampi vitakketi "
"vihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi."
msgstr "And they think sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts."

msgctxt "an4.138:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti anikaṭṭhacitto ca."
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in neither body nor mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.138:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti nikaṭṭhacitto ca?"
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in both body and mind?"

msgctxt "an4.138:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person frequents remote lodgings in the wilderness and the "
"forest."

msgctxt "an4.138:5.3"
msgid ""
"So tattha nekkhammavitakkampi vitakketi abyāpādavitakkampi vitakketi "
"avihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi."
msgstr "And they think thoughts of renunciation, love, and kindness."

msgctxt "an4.138:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti nikaṭṭhacitto ca."
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in both body and mind."

msgctxt "an4.138:5.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.138:5.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
